LIST OF DOWNTON ABBEY EPISODES Downton Abbey is a British period drama television series created by Julian Fellowes and co - produced by Carnival Films and Masterpiece .
It first aired on ITV in the United Kingdom on 26 September 2010 , and on PBS in the United States on 9 January 2011 , as part of the Masterpiece Classic anthology .
Six series have been made , the sixth airing in the autumn of 2015 in the UK and Ireland , and in January 2016 in the United States .
On 26 March 2015 , the sixth series was confirmed to be the final series , with the final episode airing in the UK on 25 December 2015 on ITV .
During the course of the programme , 52 episodes of Downton Abbey aired over six series .
On 13 July 2018 , a feature length film was confirmed , which is scheduled for a UK release on 13 September 2019 .
